Package com.ekuefler.supereventbus.multievent

Class Summary
MultiEvent An event wrapping another event that could be one of several unrelated types.
 

Annotation Types Summary
EventTypes An annotation that, when applied to a parameter of type MultiEvent, specifies which types of events that method should listen for.
